Columns.Name: CreditGrantorId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Credit Grantor.

Columns.Name: LoanAccountNumber
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a loan.

Columns.Name: LoanAmount
Columns.Description: The amount of the loan.

Columns.Name: CapitalizedLoanAmount
Columns.Description: An increase in the principal balance of a Stafford, SLS, PLUS, Federal Consolidation, or alternative loan that occurs when a lender adds the interest accrued on the loan to the outstanding balance.

Columns.Name: LoanTermMonths
Columns.Description: The term of the education loan expressed in months.

Columns.Name: InterestRatePercentage
Columns.Description: The interest rate of the loan.

Columns.Name: AprRate
Columns.Description: The APR rate of the loan.

Columns.Name: LoanApplicationDate
Columns.Description: The date that the loan was applied for.

Columns.Name: LoanGrantedDate
Columns.Description: The date that the loan was granted.

Columns.Name: LoanDisbursementDate
Columns.Description: The date that the loan is to be or was disbursed.

Columns.Name: SchoolName
Columns.Description: The name of the school to which the student is going to pay the loan funds.

Columns.Name: SchoolLocationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Location.

Columns.Name: SchoolLoanOfficerName
Columns.Description: The name of the school loan officer assigned to the case.

Columns.Name: SchoolLoanOfficerTitle
Columns.Description: The title of the school loan officer assigned to the case.

Columns.Name: SchoolOfficerTelephoneNumber
Columns.Description: The telephone number of the school loan officer assigned to the case.

Columns.Name: SchoolOfficerFaxNumber
Columns.Description: The fax number of the school loan officer assigned to the case.

Columns.Name: SchoolOfficerEmailAddress
Columns.Description: The email address of the school loan officer assigned to the case.

Columns.Name: SubsidizedLoanIndicator
Columns.Description: indicates that the loan is subsidized by a third party organization.

Columns.Name: SubsidizedByOrganizationName
Columns.Description: The name of the subsidizing organization.

Columns.Name: AutomaticPaymentIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates that payments are automatically made from an account.

Columns.Name: EducationLoanTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an education loan type.
